<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>MHFC - Matriz Holográfica de Flujo Colectivo</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-dark: #07070a;
            --neon-blue: #00f3ff;
            --neon-green: #39ff14;
            --neon-red: #ff3131;
            --gold: #ffaa00;
            --titanium: #1e1f26;
            --slate: #0d0f14;
            --text-main: #f0f3fa;
            --text-muted: #8c9bb0;
            --font-sans: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
            --font-mono: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            user-select: none;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-dark);
            color: var(--text-main);
            font-family: var(--font-sans);
            overflow: hidden;
            width: 100vw;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            position: relative;
        }

        /* Scanlines and chromatic noise for futuristic shader */
        body::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(18, 16, 16, 0) 50%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25) 50%), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.06), rgba(0, 255, 0, 0.02), rgba(0, 0, 255, 0.06));
            background-size: 100% 4px, 6px 100%;
            z-index: 100;
            pointer-events: none;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 15px 25px;
            background: rgb(13, 15, 20);
            border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(0, 243, 255, 0.15);
            z-index: 50;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
        }

        .author-tag {
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--neon-blue);
            font-weight: 500;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .author-tag::before {
            content: "";
            display: inline-block;
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            background-color: var(--neon-blue);
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--neon-blue);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: pulse-glow 1.5s infinite alternate;
        }

        .author-name {
            color: #ffffff;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
        }

        .logo-center {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .logo-center h1 {
            font-size: 15px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--text-main);
            margin-bottom: 2px;
        }

        .logo-center p {
            font-size: 10px;
            color: var(--neon-green);
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .lang-switch {
            display: flex;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 243, 255, 0.3);
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 2px;
            gap: 2px;
        }

        .lang-btn {
            background: transparent;
            border: none;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            padding: 4px 10px;
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            font-size: 11px;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 2px;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        .lang-btn.active {
            background: var(--neon-blue);
            color: var(--bg-dark);
            font-weight: bold;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 243, 255, 0.5);
        }

        /* Layout Grid */
        .app-container {
            flex: 1;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr 340px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        /* Side panels */
        .side-panel {
            background: rgba(13, 15, 20, 0.95);
            border-right: 1px solid rgba(0, 243, 255, 0.1);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            z-index: 40;
            overflow-y: auto;
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
        }

        .side-panel.right {
            border-right: none;
            border-left: 1px solid rgba(0, 243, 255, 0.1);
        }

        /* Centered 3D View */
        .viewport-container {
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #101524 0%, #030407 100%);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 243, 255, 0.05);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        canvas {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            outline: none;
            cursor: grab;
        }

        canvas:active {
            cursor: grabbing;
        }

        /* Floating HUD overlays */
        .hud-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            background: rgba(8, 10, 15, 0.85);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 243, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            pointer-events: auto;
            font-size: 11px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);
            backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
        }

        .hud-top-left {
            top: 20px;
            left: 20px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 4px;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--neon-blue);
        }

        .hud-bottom-right {
            bottom: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 6px;
            border-right: 4px solid var(--neon-green);
            text-align: right;
            min-width: 200px;
        }

        .hud-system-modes {
            bottom: 20px;
            left: 20px;
            display: flex;
            gap: 8px;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
            border: 1px dashed rgba(0,243,255,0.4);
        }

        .hud-mode-indicator {
            padding: 4px 8px;
            border-radius: 2px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            font-size: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
            border: 1px solid transparent;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        .hud-mode-indicator.active {
            background: rgba(0, 243, 255, 0.15);
            border-color: var(--neon-blue);
            color: var(--neon-blue);
            text-shadow: 0 0 5px var(--neon-blue);
        }

        /* Components Card */
        .card {
            background: rgba(20, 24, 33, 0.8);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 243, 255, 0.08);
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 15px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 12px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }

        .card::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 2px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--neon-blue), transparent);
        }

        .card-title {
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--neon-blue);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            border-bottom: 1px dashed rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            padding-bottom: 6px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        /* Controls / Buttons */
        .btn {
            background: rgba(0, 243, 255, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 243, 255, 0.3);
            color: var(--text-main);
            font-family: var(--font-sans);
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 500;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: var(--neon-blue);
            color: var(--bg-dark);
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 243, 255, 0.4);
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .btn-green {
            border-color: rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.4);
            background: rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.05);
        }

        .btn-green:hover {
            background: var(--neon-green);
            color: var(--bg-dark);
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.4);
        }

        /* Parameters state slider */
        .param-row {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 4px;
        }

        .param-label {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            font-size: 11px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
        }

        .param-val {
            color: var(--neon-blue);
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .param-slider {
            -webkit-appearance: none;
            appearance: none;
            width: 100%;
            height: 4px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 2px;
            outline: none;
        }

        .param-slider::-webkit-slider-thumb {
            -webkit-appearance: none;
            appearance: none;
            width: 12px;
            height: 12px;
            background: var(--neon-blue);
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--neon-blue);
        }

        /* Dynamic nodes visual values/bars */
        .metric-bar {
            width: 100%;
            height: 6px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border-radius: 3px;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }

        .metric-fill {
            height: 100%;
            width: 50%;
            background: var(--neon-blue);
            box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--neon-blue);
            transition: width 0.3s ease;
        }

        .metric-fill.warning {
            background: var(--neon-red);
            box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--neon-red);
        }

        .metric-fill.good {
            background: var(--neon-green);
            box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--neon-green);
        }

        /* Audio Controls */
        .audio-btn {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 20px;
            right: 250px;
            z-index: 60;
            background: rgba(13, 15, 20, 0.9);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 243, 255, 0.3);
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            cursor: pointer;
            color: var(--neon-blue);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .audio-btn:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px var(--neon-blue);
            background: var(--neon-blue);
            color: var(--bg-dark);
        }

        /* General Animations */
        @keyframes pulse-glow {
            0% {
                opacity: 0.5;
                box-shadow: 0 0 4px var(--neon-blue);
            }
            100% {
                opacity: 1;
                box-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--neon-blue);
            }
        }

        .status-badge {
            padding: 2px 6px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-size: 9px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .badge-active {
            background: rgba(0, 243, 255, 0.15);
            color: var(--neon-blue);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 243, 255, 0.3);
        }

        .badge-warning {
            background: rgba(255, 49, 49, 0.15);
            color: var(--neon-red);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 49, 49, 0.3);
        }

        .badge-good {
            background: rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.15);
            color: var(--neon-green);
            border: 1px solid rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.3);
        }

        /* Grid data visualizer */
        .interactive-graph {
            height: 80px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border-radius: 4px;
            position: relative;
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            .app-container {
                grid-template-columns: 240px 1fr;
            }
            .side-panel.right {
                display: none;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="author-tag" id="headerAuthor">
            Dr. Julio César Oporta Barrera - 100% OFFLINE
        </div>
        <div class="logo-center">
            <h1 id="appTitle">MATRIZ HOLOGRÁFICA DE FLUJO COLECTIVO</h1>
            <p id="appSubtitle">PROTOTIPO TÁCTICO DE SIMULACIÓN EN 3D</p>
        </div>
        <div class="lang-switch">
            <button class="lang-btn active" onclick="switchLanguage('es')">ES</button>
            <button class="lang-btn" onclick="switchLanguage('en')">EN</button>
            <button class="lang-btn" onclick="switchLanguage('zh')">ZH</button>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="app-container">
        <!-- Panel Izquierdo: Biomecánica & Física -->
        <div class="side-panel">
            <!-- BIOMECANICA CUANTICA -->
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-title">
                    <span id="labelBiomechanics">BIOMECÁNICA CELULAR</span>
                    <span class="status-badge badge-active" id="badgeStatus1">GNN ACTIVO</span>
                </div>
                <div class="param-row">
                    <div class="param-label">
                        <span id="labelIFM">Índice Fatiga Molecular (IFM)</span>
                        <span id="valIFM" class="param-val">34%</span>
                    </div>
                    <input type="range" id="sliderIFM" class="param-slider" min="10" max="95" value="34" oninput="updateParam('IFM')">
                    <div class="metric-bar"><div id="barIFM" class="metric-fill" style="width: 34%;"></div></div>
                </div>
                <div class="param-row">
                    <div class="param-label">
                        <span id="labelTissue">Integridad del Tejido</span>
                        <span id="valTissue" class="param-val">89%</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="metric-bar"><div id="barTissue" class="metric-fill good" style="width: 89%;"></div></div>
                </div>
                <div class="param-row">
                    <div class="param-label">
                        <span id="labelAchilles">Tensión del Tendón Aquiles</span>
                        <span id="valAchilles" class="param-val">Low</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- FISICA MODULAR & ENERGIA HIBRIDA -->
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-title">
                    <span id="labelModularPhysics">FÍSICA & ENERGÍA</span>
                    <span class="status-badge badge-good">ESTABLE</span>
                </div>
                <div class="param-row">
                    <div class="param-label">
                        <span id="labelMito">Resonancia Mitocondrial</span>
                        <span id="valMito" class="param-val">94%</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="metric-bar"><div class="metric-fill good" style="width: 94%;"></div></div>
                </div>
                <div class="param-row">
                    <div class="param-label">
                        <span id="labelEnergy">Energía Híbrida</span>
                        <span id="valEnergy" class="param-val">82 kWH</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- BOTONES DE CONTROL DE SIMULACION -->
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-title" id="labelControls">Controles del Simulador</div>
                <button class="btn btn-green" id="btnPlay" onclick="toggleSim()">INICIAR SIMULACIÓN</button>
                <button class="btn" id="btnReset" onclick="resetSim()">REINICIAR VALORES</button>
                <button class="btn" id="btnScenario" onclick="runAttackScenario()">JUGADA DEFENSIVA</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Panel Central: 3D Holographic Stage -->
        <div class="viewport-container" id="viewContainer">
            <!-- Tactical Overlays -->
            <div class="hud-overlay hud-top-left">
                <div style="font-weight: bold; color: var(--neon-blue);">MHFC REALTIME FEED</div>
                <div>AUTOR: <span class="author-name">Dr. Julio César Oporta Barrera</span></div>
                <div>LATENCIA: <span style="color: var(--neon-green)">1.2ms</span></div>
                <div id="hudNodes">SINOPSIS IA: 5 NODOS ENLAZADOS</div>
            </div>

            <div class="hud-overlay hud-bottom-right">
                <div id="hudMPE" style="font-weight: bold; color: var(--neon-blue);">MPE SCENARIO EVALUATION</div>
                <div>SEC: <span style="color: var(--gold)" id="hudPlay">Fórmula Ofensiva 4-A</span></div>
                <div>COHERENCIA COGNITIVA: <span style="color: var(--neon-green)" id="valCoherencia">94%</span></div>
                <div>FACTOR ENTRÓPICO: <span style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7)" id="valEntropico">2.41</span></div>
            </div>

            <!-- Operating Modes Indicators -->
            <div class="hud-overlay hud-system-modes">
                <div class="hud-mode-indicator active" id="modeActivo" onclick="setOpMode('activo')">ACTIVO</div>
                <div class="hud-mode-indicator" id="modeRecup" onclick="setOpMode('recup')">REGENERACIÓN</div>
                <div class="hud-mode-indicator" id="modeSim" onclick="setOpMode('sim')">SIMULACIÓN</div>
                <div class="hud-mode-indicator" id="modeEmerg" onclick="setOpMode('emerg')">SOBRECARGA</div>
            </div>

            <!-- Canvas for custom robust 3D math engine -->
            <canvas id="canvas3d"></canvas>
        </div>

        <!-- Panel Derecho: Coherencia & Predicción -->
        <div class="side-panel right">
            <!-- SINERGIA DE FLUJO TACTICO -->
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-title">
                    <span id="labelTacticalFlow">FLUJO TÁCTICO (SFT)</span>
                    <span class="status-badge badge-active" id="badgeStatus2">SINCRÓNICO</span>
                </div>
                <div class="param-row">
                    <div class="param-label">
                        <span id="labelICC">Coherencia Colectiva (ICC)</span>
                        <span id="valICC" class="param-val">84%</span>
                    </div>
                    <input type="range" id="sliderICC" class="param-slider" min="20" max="100" value="84" oninput="updateParam('ICC')">
                    <div class="metric-bar"><div id="barICC" class="metric-fill" style="width: 84%;"></div></div>
                </div>
                <div class="param-row">
                    <div class="param-label">
                        <span id="labelVCC">Conflicto Cognitivo (VCC)</span>
                        <span id="valVCC" class="param-val">12%</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="metric-bar"><div id="barVCC" class="metric-fill warning" style="width: 12%;"></div></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- MOTOR DE PREDICCION ENTROPICA -->
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-title">
                    <span id="labelPred">PREDICCIÓN ENTRÓPICA</span>
                    <span class="status-badge badge-good">MPE ESTADÍSTICO</span>
                </div>
                <div class="param-row">
                    <div class="param-label">
                        <span id="labelFFE">Factor Entrópico (FFE)</span>
                        <span id="valFFE" class="param-val">2.84</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="param-row">
                    <span id="labelRealtimeGraph" style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-muted); font-family: var(--font-mono)">FLUJO EN TIEMPO REAL:</span>
                    <div class="interactive-graph">
                        <canvas id="canvasGraph" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; pointer-events: none;"></canvas>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- DRAFT EVALUATION -->
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-title" id="labelScoutTitle">EVALUACIÓN DE COHESIÓN</div>
                <p style="font-size: 11.5px; line-height: 1.4; color: var(--text-muted);" id="scoutDesc">
                    Predice cómo un prospecto altera el Índice de Coherencia Colectiva (ICC) del equipo titular en un 72%.
                </p>
                <div style="font-size: 11px; font-family: var(--font-mono); color: var(--neon-green)">
                    +12.4% IMPACTO PROYECTADO
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Toggle Ambient sound feedback -->
    <div class="audio-btn" onclick="toggleAudio()" title="Activar Sonido Táctico Offline">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <polygon points="11 5 6 9 2 9 2 15 6 15 11 19 11 5"></polygon>
            <path d="M19.07 4.93a10 10 0 0 1 0 14.14M15.54 8.46a5 5 0 0 1 0 7.07"></path>
        </svg>
    </div>

